<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero-section">
    <h1 class="hero-title fade-in-up">Welcome to Aikido Library</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle fade-in-up-delay">Discover the art and spirit of Aikido through our comprehensive digital dojo</p>
</section>

<!-- Welcome Content -->
<div class="card fade-in-up">
    <h2 class="card-title">🥋 Embark on Your Aikido Journey</h2>
    <div class="card-content">
        <p>Embark on a journey of discovery and mastery with Aikido Library, your premier online destination dedicated to the art and spirit of Aikido. Here, we fuse tradition with innovation, offering an extensive collection of resources for both the seasoned practitioner and the curious beginner.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Feature Cards -->
<div class="library-grid">
    <div class="card fade-in-up">
        <h3 class="card-title">🎯 Explore the Essence</h3>
        <div class="card-content">
            <p>At Aikido Library, we delve deep into the heart of Aikido, presenting an art form that transcends mere physical techniques. Our platform is a treasure trove of knowledge, from the historical roots of Aikido to its modern interpretations and applications.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card fade-in-up-delay">
        <h3 class="card-title">🏛️ Your Virtual Dojo</h3>
        <div class="card-content">
            <p>Our comprehensive digital dojo features a vast array of training materials, instructional videos, and detailed guides. Whether you're perfecting your technique, learning new katas, or exploring the philosophical underpinnings of Aikido, our library is designed to guide you every step of the way.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card fade-in-up">
        <h3 class="card-title">🌍 Community and Connection</h3>
        <div class="card-content">
            <p>Join a vibrant community of Aikido enthusiasts from around the globe. Share experiences, gain insights, and connect with fellow practitioners. At Aikido Library, we believe in growing together, fostering a space where knowledge, ideas, and passion for Aikido flourish.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card fade-in-up-delay">
        <h3 class="card-title">📱 Accessible Anytime, Anywhere</h3>
        <div class="card-content">
            <p>With a focus on accessibility, Aikido Library brings the world of Aikido to your fingertips. Access our resources anytime, anywhere, and embark on a learning journey that fits your pace and style.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Call to Action -->
